file.name: issue-11340.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.3"
info:
  title: Issue 11340 - Bean Validation Breaks Generated Java Code
  version: "1.0.2"
  description: With Bean Validation @NotNull and type of parameter must be separated by space.
paths:
  /configuration:
    put:
      operationId: operation
      description: Operation with required header and required request body
      parameters:
        - in: header
          name: x-non-null-header-parameter
          schema:
            type: string
          required: true
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              minProperties: 1
              additionalProperties:
                type: object
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
